content: Amazing, baby lifesaver. Worked every time to calm my boy without fail.
Works like a champ when all else fails. Just turn the app on as soon as baby opens eyes, she's instantly distracted and out of her bad place.
Worth all 149 pennies. Works great when baby is over tired and can't stop crying. Turn this on and in five minutes his head is nodding and in ten he's out like a light!
Life SAVER
The name could not be more fitting. ❤️
Always calms my son when needed ^-^

This is the greatest app I've ever found for little ones. I was looking for something to keep my 3 month old occupied for just a moment, downloaded every app for babies I could find, and THIS IS IT! She was calm and happy enough for me to take a shower. Absolutely had to buy the upgraded version. All before I realized that it interacts and adds color when you touch the screens (not positive if thats just after you pay, but well worth it if it is). Now my 3 year old loves it too.

I felt the need to buy this version because the free version is so good! My 5 month is teething and woke up screaming. This was the only thing that calmed him down before sending him back to sleep. This app is simply amazing!
Works great for my baby!

I initially purchased the upgraded version specifically so I could have the child lock that would prevent my kid from getting out of the app. Now, I no longer have the option to enable it. Really disappointing as this was one of the only cheap apps with that option.
replyContent: Update 2019-12-19:  The child lock feature is back with the latest update.  Sorry it probably came too late for help with your little one.

content:

Awesome! We'll worth $1.49 (and I never purchase apps!)!

Absolute treasure for a six month old. Keeps her occupied and distracted for short periods. That is so helpful as a parent. Its also calming to listen to the classical music. I was surprised The Entertainer wasn't a background tune. Saves daddy just as much as mummy!
Wasn't opening, but a developer helped me troubleshoot it (uninstall then reinstall... Yes,  I should have tried that.) Thank you!! This app is worth every star!!!
replyContent:
I recommend uninstalling and reinstalling.  It's free to re-install once you've bought the app once.

I think this will fix the issue.  I will investigate to see if there's any other potential causes of this problem.

content: Baby loves it. Thank you.
Keeps my 2 weeks old busy and intrigued while changing her diaper... No more kicking! UPDATE: at now 2 month, the cutie still loves it and sings with it!
My granddaughter loves this! It calms her down real quick. She gets completely enthralled.
Baby will go from screaming to placid within seconds. Extraordinary and exceptional value too. Only request would be to have a few more songs. Otherwise perfect
Nothing else like it for babies!
I would be lost without this app!
But why the child lock not working? On my lg g4
replyContent: Thanks for the feedback.  A fix has now been submitted.  It should now work on most devices.

content: I had this app a while back and when i saw there was a paid version, i didnt even hesitate to get it. Both my daughters love it! The only thing i would ask is that there have a child lock-its easy for my girls to exit the app by hitting the home/back buttons

I had the lite version before there was a paid version. I upgraded as soon as I realized the paid version came out. No intrusive adds in the lite. I also requested a feature and the dev got back to me within 2 hours. Awesome. Great app my son loves it.

I've been using the original version since my 6 mo was only a few weeks old. She loves it!! This app is truly a mommy saver and I recommend it to all my mommy forum friends. I will be buying the next app when it comes out. So so so so excited!

I'm so happy a new version was created my 7 month old son loves the original or "lite" version. Thank you so much. A+ game for babies! Definatly worth getting very happy with other song selections. Although whenever my son hears the original he knows and gets excited it's coming ;)
I and my 6 month old son LOVE this app. We had the lite version and jumped at the chance to buy this version! Will definitely be keeping an eye out for more apps.
replyContent: :) Thanks for the great rating and support!  I try to make it as good as I can (It was made for my own son before I shared it).  More updated versions are coming soon, and hopefully another app early next year.  Happy parenting!
